This is Fabric.


To Build:
1. download and build polyglot
2. set $POLYGLOT to your polyglot directory
3. run ant

To Compile an application:
use the fabc script, or run fabric.Main with java, e.g.:
java fabric.Main tests/OO7/*.fab -d rt-classes -sourcepath src/runtime:tests -sigcp sig-classes

To Run a core:
use the core script, or run fabric.core.Main with java, e.g.:
java fabric.core.Main --core core0 etc/keys/core0.keystore etc/keys/trust.keystore password

To Run an application:
use the fab script, or run fabric.client.Client with java, e.g.:
java fabric.client.Client OO7.Benchmark fab://core0/OO7 tiny 3
java fabric.client.Client OO7.traversals.T1 fab://core0/OO7 --hot

